# FlowCanvas Architecture Rules

## Project Identity
FlowCanvas is an org-wide spatial task management web app. The entire application lives on an infinite canvas (like Figma) powered by ReactFlow. The canvas is THE product. Everything else is chrome around it.

## Tech Stack (LOCKED — do not suggest alternatives)
- Framework: Next.js 15 App Router with TypeScript strict mode
- Canvas Engine: @xyflow/react v12 (ReactFlow)
- State: Zustand (canvas state) + TanStack Query v5 (server state)
- Styling: Tailwind CSS v4 — utility classes only, no CSS-in-JS
- Real-time: Yjs + y-websocket for CRDT-based collaborative canvas sync
- Backend: Node.js + Fastify v5 + @fastify/websocket
- Database: PostgreSQL 16 + Drizzle ORM
- Auth: better-auth with JWT
- File Storage: Cloudflare R2
- Charts: Recharts (dashboard only)
- Animations: Framer Motion (UI panels only — NOT on canvas nodes)
- Icons: Lucide React (never Material Symbols — Stitch used them, we don't)

## Structural Rules
1. Canvas components live in src/components/canvas/ — they are ReactFlow nodes/edges/handles only
2. Panel components live in src/components/panels/ — they are sidebar/inspector UI
3. Dashboard components live in src/components/dashboard/ — charts and KPIs only
4. All shared primitives (Button, Badge, Chip, Avatar) live in src/components/ui/
5. ALL business logic lives in src/lib/ — never inline in components
6. CPM algorithm lives in src/lib/cpm/ — pure TypeScript, zero dependencies, fully tested
7. Zustand stores live in src/stores/ — one store per domain (canvas, ui, user, projects)
8. ALL TypeScript types live in src/types/ — no inline type declarations in components
9. Server code lives in server/ — it is a SEPARATE process from the Next.js frontend

## Import Rules
- Always use path aliases: @/components, @/lib, @/stores, @/types
- Never import server/ code into src/ — they are separate processes
- Never import ReactFlow internals directly — always wrap in canvas/ components

## Naming Conventions
- React components: PascalCase
- Hooks: useXxx
- Stores: useXxxStore
- Types/Interfaces: PascalCase, no I prefix
- Constants: SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE
- Files: kebab-case for all non-component files
